	   <tr><td colspan=2>I'm entirely new to this game, Help me out a bit please, Barbarian, Dark Elf, Dwarf, Gnome, Halfling, Half Elf, Human, WoodElf? I'm awaiting an answer or two.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
